Package: saveLavaanPlot
Type: Package
Title: Make and save plots with lavaanPlot
Version: 0.2.1
Author: Jasmijn Bazen
Maintainer: Jasmijn Bazen <j.l.bazen@students.uu.nl>
Description: Saves a Structural Equation Model (SEM) plot generated by lavaanPlot. The function handles intermediate steps, including exporting the plot to SVG and converting to PNG.
